trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of interfaces for use in Web Parts connections.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de interfaces para su uso en conexiones de elementos web.

trans-unit.source: Communication between a provider and consumer requires a contract defined in an interface.
trans-unit.target: La comunicación entre un proveedor y un consumidor requiere un contrato definido en una interfaz.

trans-unit.source: This collection contains all the communication interfaces supported by the consumer.
trans-unit.target: Esta colección contiene todas las interfaces de comunicación admitidas por el consumidor.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProviderConnectionPoint.GetSecondaryInterfaces%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method returns a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: El método <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProviderConnectionPoint.GetSecondaryInterfaces%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> devuelve un objeto <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A collection of objects to convert into a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Colección de objetos que se va a convertir en una colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class with the specified collection.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> con la colección especificada.

trans-unit.source: An object in <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> cannot be added to a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto incluido en <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> no se puede agregar a una colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> to combine with the <c>connectionInterfaces</c> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> que se va a combinar con el objeto <c>connectionInterfaces</c>.

trans-unit.source: A collection to combine with the <c>existingConnectionInterfaces</c> object.
trans-unit.target: Colección que se va a combinar con el objeto <c>existingConnectionInterfaces</c>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class by combining the two specified collections.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> combinando las dos colecciones especificadas.

trans-unit.source: An object in <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> cannot be added to a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Un objeto incluido en <paramref name="connectionInterfaces" /> no se puede agregar a una colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The type to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Tipo que se va a buscar en <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> object contains a specific value.
trans-unit.target: Determina si el objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> contiene un valor específico.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="value" /> is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si <paramref name="value" /> se encuentra en la matriz <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />; en caso contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional que constituye el destino de los elementos copiados de <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: La matriz <see cref="T:System.Array" /> debe tener una indización de base cero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero de <c>array</c> donde comienza la copia.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" /> object to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todo el objeto <see cref="T:System.Collections.ReadOnlyCollectionBase" /> en una matriz <see cref="T:System.Array" /> unidimensional y compatible, a partir del índice especificado de la matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: References a static, read-only instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Hace referencia a una instancia estática de sólo lectura de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The type to locate in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Tipo que se va a buscar en la colección.

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified object and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Busca el objeto especificado y devuelve el índice de base cero de la primera aparición en toda la colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first occurrence of <paramref name="value" /> within the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero de la primera aparición de <paramref name="value" /> en la totalidad de <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ConnectionInterfaceCollection" />, si se encuentra; en caso contrario, -1.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the element to get.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero del elemento que se va a obtener.

trans-unit.source: Gets the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el elemento en el índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Elemento en el índice especificado.
